  "libraryVersion": "2025.06",
  "lastValidated": "2026-06-27",
  "pluginNotes": "Token is a SAP instance. Composed by Tokenizer or MultiInput \u2014 specs typically don't emit Token directly. If a spec does emit Token, the plugin places the SAP instance via SAP_KEYS. Text is injected via setProperties or findOne(TEXT).",
